RS Components has signed a distribution agreement with IDEC EMEA, a manufacturer of industrial automation and control products. RS Components is the first distributor in Europe to stock the IDEC range, which includes over 1,000 components. The products include more than 700 new industrial control switches with 16mm and 22mm diameters, as well as safety switches, safety laser scanners, power supplies, and industrial LED lights. “We are delighted to now add IDEC products to the RS portfolio,” said IDEC. “The high-quality industrial nature of the IDEC product range will resonate well with our core customers across all markets,” said RS Components.